# AI Data Analyst Dashboard

An AI-powered web application that allows users to upload datasets (CSV/Excel) and ask questions in natural language to get instant insights, summaries, and visualizations.

---

## Features

- Upload CSV and Excel files
- Ask questions in natural language (AI-powered)
- Automatic chart generation (Bar, Line, Pie)
- AI-generated insights and summaries
- Download full analysis report (PDF)
- Fast and interactive dashboard UI
- Smart column detection (dynamic datasets)

---

## Note on PDF Support

PDF support is limited due to unstructured data formats.

For best results, use CSV or Excel files.

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend

- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- Chart.js

### Backend

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Groq API (LLaMA 3)

### Other Tools

- Multer (file upload)
- XLSX (Excel parsing)
- csv-parser
- jsPDF (report generation)

